# Copy to .env and fill in. Written automatically by `npm run init` — you
# normally don't need to edit this by hand.

# ElevenLabs API key — required only if you don't provide your own MP3
# narration (the pipeline falls back to ElevenLabs v3 TTS).
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# There is deliberately NO ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID here.
#
# The narration voice is chosen per video, from the list in
# <workspace>/voices.json (scripts/voice-library.mjs). This file used to seed
# every fresh install with FHhpndubmejSghqiumSv — "thu-le-vn", a voice its own
# publisher describes as cloned for cross-lingual INDONESIAN TTS. Nobody chose
# it; it was a default that outlived its reason and then quietly became the
# voice new machines shipped with.
#
# Machines set up before the voice library still have this key, and it is
# honoured: voice-library.mjs migrates it into voices.json on first use.
